comments.body:
@TomSweeneyRedHat Somehow your empty dir PR got in, and now all upstream merges are blocked by the same failure.

Basically we have a dockerignore test that is supposed to fail when a COPY copies nothing from a directory.  Since your PR allows empty directories to be COPIED, this no longer fails, so the test for failure is failing.  
@test "bud with .dockerignore"  in bud.bats

How this got into master, I do not know.  But maybe the test should just be removed.
